      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOCKERY MIRAGE (1) settled well back early on debut and but the line nicely when second (20.14) at this track over 366m. Boxed the fence this time. Likely to improve sharply this time. HARA'S LOKI (2) has a solid record despite not breaking through for a win in 21 starts. Hasn't been able to break through recently but continues to race well, filling the minors at the last four starts. Well placed and gets his chance. MARIJA (7) comes off an average run last start when fourth at this track over 366m behind Raptor Girl (20.40). Has the ability to give this a shake. GOLDEN ART (8) is a Robert Ayres-trained newcomer by Feral Franky out of Stop Watch. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Profiles nicely and can feature in the finish.",
